All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
BrushShape
Brush which draws thick paint with primary color
CanvasUpdateEvent
Event class for Canvas-related event such as mouse position change, resize, modify
CanvasUpdateListener
Event listener interface for Canvas update events such as resize, modify, etc.
ColorPaletteToolbar
Toolbar containing a color palette from primary colors and a Primary and Secondary color selector
EllipseShape
Ellipse shape to draw oval and circle
Eraser
Eraser to fill image with squares of secondary color
ImageInstance
Holds information of current file user is working on
ImageSizeDialog
Simple dialog box for assigning dimension to image
LineShape
Straight line between starting and ending points
PaintEx
This class creates a new PaintEx application window and begins the application.
PaintExCanvas
The white canvas to draw the image with various shapes and brushes
PaintExEventMulticaster
Allows multiple event listeners to be added to the event dispatcher class.
PaintExWindow
Main window that contains tools, menu, canvas status bar, etc.
PencilShape
Pencil to draw path from start point continuously through the end point
RectangleShape
Rectangle shape to draw rectangle or square
Shape
General class to store information needed to draw any kind of shape
ShapeFactory
Factory class to return shape object based on the tool selected, and applies the properties to the shape
StatusInfo
This class creates a status tool bar at bottom of the screen and shows common information like mouse position
SwatchType
Which type of color is selected from the color toolbar
ToolBar
Toolbar to show actions and shapes for image manipulation
ToolBar.ColorFillStyle
Draw with outline, fill or both
ToolBar.ImageActionType
Action to perform on image
ToolBar.PaintToolType
Buttons for various tools
ToolbarEvent
Event class for Toolbar event such as action (save, open) or tool select (pencil, brush)
ToolbarListener
Event listener for ToolbarEvent called by various toolbar buttons
